  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5385018">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5385018/" class="title-link">写这种书还是应该好奇心重些</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5385018"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/roulong/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3486559-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/roulong/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">一大坨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-12"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-12 00:56:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5385018_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一本写武器与防护装备的书，怎能不满足读者对武器杀伤程度的好奇心，对甲胄防护能力的测试呢？影视作品里甲胄基本没用，一刀一个，没用怎么会高度发达呢，刀取代剑除了制造工艺简化之外，那么同等力度的劈砍杀伤程度有多大不同？鳞甲与锁子甲明光铠对同等力度的箭防护能力有何...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5385018_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5385018_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










